===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|weyfaren|lang=enm}}, originally in participle form {{term|weyfarand|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|weġfarende||wayfaring}}, equivalent to {{compound|way|faring|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|vejfarende||wayfaring|lang=da}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|vägfarande||lang=sv}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|vegfarandi||wayfaring|lang=is}}. More at {{l|en|way}}, {{l|en|fare}}.

